The paper discusses testing methodologies for AI applications, which is a subfield of software engineering (cs.SE) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the challenges of testing AI applications in real-world systems, which can fall under the categories of control systems (cs.SY) and computer security (cs.CR). Finally, the paper provides an example of testing face recognition applications, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV).
